"<br>"
"<ul>"
"<li><b>Enabled</b>: Show all animations completely.</li>"
"<li><b>Disabled</b>: Never show animations, show the start image only.</li>"
"<li><b>Show only once</b>: Show all animations completely but do not repeat "
